\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"ef1e3309-ce4f-4603-930e-eb872634e5f7\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"820abced-8ac3-4707-b0d2-d5d646045d45\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-20T10:11:57.087662779Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\\\"\"6E92ZMYYFZ\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"67c96682-916a-441b-85fa-b50724204384\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"113811cb-c611-41cc-b873-ab21bae7e2f3\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-20T10:12:39.966188352Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-1", "productcatalogservice-2", "frontend-0", "productcatalogservice-1", "productcatalogservice-0"], "service_name": ["frontend", "productcatalogservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-06", "aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-04"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-20T10:10:24Z to 2025-06-20T10:30:24Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-20 10:10:24+00:00 to 2025-06-20 10:30:24+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于UUID为5cb1626b-401的异常调用链数据分析，以下是主要的异常发现：\n\n1. **延迟指标：**\n   - `productcatalogservice` 在多个调用场景下都出现显著延迟，尤其是在 `frontend` 调用 `productcatalogservice` 的场景中延迟显著增加。比如：\n     - `frontend-2` 调用 `productcatalogservice-2`时，异常期间平均延迟高达39,333,334微秒，而正常平均延迟为9,500微秒，延迟增加明显。\n\n2. **错误状态：**\n   - `productcatalogservice` 多次出现 `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`。\n   - 在 `checkoutservice` 中，Order失败由于产品无法获取，比如`\"failed to prepare order: failed to get product #\"66VCHSJNUP\"`。\n\n3. **调用关系：**\n   - 主要异常路径为 `frontendservice->productcatalogservice`。\n   \n基于以上异常数据和调用拓扑结构推断如下：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"frontendservice->productcatalogservice\", \"error_ratio\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"延迟显著增加，前端调用ProductCatalogService时的异常时间平均延迟超出正常范围超过4,000倍（例如，从9,500微秒增加到39,333,334微秒）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"多次出现 `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`，影响下游服务的正常调用\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 结论\n经过分析可以确定，异常的主要来源是 `productcatalogservice`，其处理出现显著延迟并伴随地域不可用错误，直接影响到依赖其的 `frontend` 以及其他服务的正常运作。建议进一步检查 `productcatalogservice` 的数据库或集群状态，特别是地域可用性方面。", "log_analysis_findings": "根据分析UUID为5cb1626b-401的故障日志数据，可以识别出以下几种系统中的异常：\n\n### 主要异常模式\n\n1. **Region Unavailability**:\n   - 出现于多个日志条目中，涉及 `frontend` 和 `productcatalogservice` 服务。\n   - 具体错误类型：`Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`。\n   - 这是一个常见问题，表明系统可能面临一定的资源访问障碍，造成相关服务无法正常工作。问题的根源似乎在于区域无法被访问，影响了商品推荐和查询。\n\n### 关键词与模式识别\n\n### 关键词提取:\n- **错误类型**: `Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable`\n- **服务日志标签**: `frontend--region_unavailable`, `productcatalogservice--region_unavailable`\n- **类名/方法名**: 未明确标识的类名，但涉及 `rpc error`\n\n### 特定故障模式:\n- 没有检测到 DNS 故障或端口配置错误等特殊故障模式。\n\n### 证据片段:\n来自 `frontend` 和 `productcatalogservice` 服务的日志：\n- `{\"error\":\"failed to get product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info (#PHOTO202): rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"}`\n\n### 组件影响:\n- **受影响组件**: `frontend`, `productcatalogservice`\n- **根因假设**: 区域资源访问问题\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Region is unavailable - Error 9005 (HY000) affects product information retrieval\",\n      \"evidence\": \"{\\\"message\\\":\\\"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\\\",\\\"severity\\\":\\\"warning\\\",\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2025-06-20T10:11:06.088119444Z\\\"}\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Failed to retrieve product recommendations due to region unavailability\",\n      \"evidence\": \"{\\\"error\\\":\\\"failed to get product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info (#PHOTO202): rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\\\",\\\"http.req.method\\\":\\\"GET\\\",\\\"http.req.path\\\":\\\"/cart\\\"}\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n建议检查区域资源访问配置，确保区域服务的正常挂载，并验证相关网络路径的可达性，确保无误配置或资源限制。可能需要进行区域网络或数据库连接情况的深入调查。", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据获取的数据，我进行以下分析以识别故障的根本原因。\n\n### 检测到的异常指标\n\n- `client_error_ratio`\n- `duration_99th`\n- `error_ratio`\n- `failed_query_ops`\n- `memory_usage`\n- `pod_cpu_usage`\n- `rrt`\n- `server_error_ratio`\n- `store_unhealth_count`\n\n### 异常关键信息\n\n1. **TiDB 组件故障**\n   - **组件**: `tidb-tidb`\n   - **异常指标**: `failed_query_ops`, `duration_99th`\n   - **根因**: `failed_query_ops` 指标大幅上升，表明数据库查询失败次数增加，同时 `duration_99th` 的显著增高说明查询耗时增加，可能导致上层服务超时。\n   - **证据**: `failed_query_ops` 在故障期间 P99 值从 0 上升到 55.22，并且 `duration_99th` 的变化从 0.01 到 64.88。\n\n2. **Frontend 服务问题**\n   - **组件**: `frontend-0`, `frontend-1`, `frontend-2`\n   - **异常指标**: `server_error_ratio`, `error_ratio`\n   - **根因**: `frontend` 服务的多个 Pods 的 `server_error_ratio` 和 `error_ratio` 指标显著升高，表明该服务在处理请求时出错。\n   - **证据**: `frontend-0` 的 `server_error_ratio` 从 0 到 33.33，`frontend-1` 的从 0 到 31.12，以及 `frontend-2` 的从 0 到 24.5。\n\n3. **Product Catalog Service 故障**\n   - **组件**: `productcatalogservice-2`\n   - **异常指标**: `rrt`\n   - **根因**: `rrt` (请求响应时间) 指标显著升高，意味着该服务在请求处理中延迟显著。\n   - **证据**: `rrt` 的 median 从 6955.12 增加到 19975422.23。\n\n### 可能的根本原因\n\n- TiDB 数据库组件的性能下降影响到数据请求处理，导致请求延迟和失败。\n- `frontend` 服务处理请求时出现错误，增加用户报告的错误比率。\n- 上游服务 `productcatalogservice` 由于响应延迟高可能受 TiDB 故障影响。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"duration_99th\", \"error_ratio\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"memory_usage\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"store_unhealth_count\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"高 failed_query_ops 与 duration_99th 表明数据库查询性能问题。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed_query_ops 从 0 增加到 55.22; duration_99th 从 0.01 增加到 64.88。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"server_error_ratio 指标显著升高表明请求处理有严重错误。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio 从 0 到 33.33。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio 指标显著升高，表明多个请求出错。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio 从 0 增加到 31.12。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio 指标升高，可能影响服务稳定性。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio 从 0 增加到 24.5。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt 指标显著升高，表明服务响应变慢。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt 从 6955.12 增加到 19975422.23。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
